    Singly linked list implementation of JImmutableStack that stores and retrieves values in the reverse order of the corresponding add() method calls. If forward or random access to stored values is required use JImmutableArrayList or JImmutableTreeList instead, but this class is significantly faster when its limitations are acceptable.
